beer.beer_description: Like that forever partner, or the hero behind the wicket, this one is a keeper. We herald the keepers and raise them this glass of surreptitious cerebral assassin. It will please. It will go down with hints of plum and raisin, encompassed in a malty hug that the most stoic of all keepers couldn't resist. It will sink ships and loosen lips. Tall stories of wickets conquered will be told. It will finish dry, like all beached ships must. At the end of the day, The Keeper will always be there for you.
